          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Love, Indus is incomplete without its integral and powerful comma.</p><p>A soft pause. A quick escape.<br/>A symbol of continuity. An indicator of flow.<br/>An upside-down drop. Something of nature.<br/>A celebration of diversity. A confluence of cultures.</p><p>Above all, Love, Indus is a letter that can be read and re-read, and an invitation for you to write and re-write your story.</p><p>It’s all in the name.</p>",
